commitResults.messageBody:
-Add greet functionality
-Add exit functionality
-Refactor chatbot name
- Add echo functionality to echo user input

- Add adding functionality of task
- Add list functionality to list all added tasks

- Remove echo functionality as it is not needed anymore
- Added Task class to manage the task being marked or unmarked
- Added TaskList class to manage tasks

-Change Task to abstract
-Add ToDoTask which extends Task
-Add EventTask which extends Task and takes in from and to dates
-Add Deadlines which extends Task and take in by date

-Change runtest.sh to be executable
-Update input.txt to include more test cases
-Update EXPECTED.TXT to reflect the  UI changes

-Added DukeException
-Added empty description error handling and wrong command error handling
-Update text-ui-test to test for error handling

-Changed from array to arraylist collections
-Updated EXPECTED.TXT to reflect input.txt change
-Updated input.txt to test for delete
-Updated Duke.java to handle delete

-Add enum for TaskTypes
-Add enum for ModifyTask

Change spacing of switch statements

switch statements need to follow the correct coding standard and indentation.

Add saveTask

Saves serialisable objects to the specified txt file in the filepath.

Add loadTask

Loads serialisable objects from specified txt file in the filepath.

Add Task to implement Serializable

To allow Task object to be saved as objects.

Add saveTask method from Storage

To allow task to be loaded to the txt file every time the task changes.

Add loadTask method from Storage

To loadTask the first time taskList is instantiated.

Add Storage feature to main branch

This allow a txt file to store all inputs for data persistence.

Change date to a localdate object

Allow the customisation of what datestring to print out.

Change string representation

Previously returns a formatter instead of the date string that uses the formatter.

Add parsed date to the deadline task

This allows the date format printed to be correct.
